     Chadha, speaking in Hong Kong, says Indian companies may increase earnings by as much as 25 percent this year, with first-quarter results suggesting that profit growth is "on track".  (Source: Bloomberg)
  
                   
    

                 
           
                           
                 
                 
                                       
                                   
               
                        
           
